00:30:54.430 --> 00:30:56.240
There are many, many
readers, and some writers

00:30:56.240 --> 00:30:57.710
of all degrees of ability.

00:30:57.710 --> 00:30:59.180
But, you know, it was
a great place --

00:30:59.180 --> 00:31:01.200
