some point, and they get up,

00:45:22.850 --> 00:45:25.170
go to the bathroom, get the
drink, take the dog for a walk.

00:45:25.170 --> 00:45:26.470
Some of them don't come back,

00:45:26.470 --> 00:45:28.200
